Their family histories,

67
00:06:02,279 --> 00:06:04,489
what their thoughts
were on why they did it,

68
00:06:04,573 --> 00:06:07,659
when they were aroused during
the killings, that sort of thing.

69
00:06:07,742 --> 00:06:10,579
