your findings within the FBI.

72
00:06:14,249 --> 00:06:16,293
- I mean, maybe even turn it into a book.
- A book?

73
00:06:16,376 --> 00:06:18,879
Whoa. We appreciate
the vote of confidence,

74
00:06:18,962 --> 00:06:21,339
but we weren't allowed
to send you those notes.

75
00:06:21,423 --> 00:06:24,342
- We can't publicize what we're doing.
- [CARR] Why not?

76
00:06:24,426 --> 00:06:26,303
[TENCH] Our department
head gave us weekends only

77
00:06:26,386 --> 00:06:27,887
and an office in the basement.

78
00:06:27,971 --> 00:06:30,390
