131
00:08:54,451 --> 00:08:57,370
then you should talk to someone who
has the freedom and resources to...

132
00:08:57,454 --> 00:08:59,122
[TENCH] We'll stick with it for now.

133
00:08:59,205 --> 00:09:01,708
It'll be slow going, but
we're not ready to give up yet.

134
00:09:01,791 --> 00:09:02,959
Of course not.

135
00:09:03,043 --> 00:09:06,337
But it's good to get some encouragement,
even if our hands are tied.

136
00:09:07,005 --> 00:09:08,039
Thank you.

137
00:09:08,673 --> 00:09:09,832
It's a pleasure.

138
00:09:11,618 --> 00:09:12,635
- What if...
- Don't.

139
00:09:12,719 --> 00:09:14,137
- I'm just saying we could...
- Holden.

140
00:09:16,890 --> 00:09:18,641
Look, I'm frustrated too.

141
00:09:21,352 --> 00:09:23,038
You know, they shoot
the birds in the yard

142
