Speck in Illinois.

192
00:12:09,354 --> 00:12:12,440
- Great, we can do a Midwest sweep.
- Gerard John Schaefer.

193
00:12:12,523 --> 00:12:15,568
He killed at least 30, they
think. That was in Florida, though.

194
00:12:15,652 --> 00:12:17,487
I can't say no to a Florida golf course.

195
00:12:17,570 --> 00:12:20,156
[PHONE RINGING]

196
00:12:26,855 --> 00:12:27,914
Bill Tench.

197
00:12:27,997 --> 00:12:30,750
- <i>Hey, Bill. It's Roy Carver.</i>
- Hey, Roy. What can I do for you?

198
00:12:30,833 --> 00:12:33,002
<i>We need to talk. There's
been another attack.</i>

199
00:12:33,086 --> 00:12:34,671
<i>This time resulting in a fatality.</i>

200
00:12:36,881 --> 00:12:39,008
- Got it. <i>
- Can I get you guys back out here?</i>

201
00:12:39,092 --> 00:12:40,843
Okay. Let me get back to you.

202
00:12:42,845 --> 00:12:44,847
- What's up?
- Carver.

203
00:12:44,931 --> 00:12:45,931
Been another one.

204
00:12:45,932 --> 00:12:48,768
Same age as Rosemary Gonzales,
only this time she's dead.

205
00:12:50,436 --> 00:12:53,189
Bill, my God! We're vindicated.

206
00:12:53,272 --> 00:12:55,775
What's the matter with you?
An old lady was just murdered.

207
00:12:59,278 --> 00:13:00,989
We can talk to Kemper again.

208
00:13:07,203 --> 00:13:09,497
Did she have a dog? Please
tell me there's a dog.

209
00:13:09,580 --> 00:13:12,166
A bigger dog. Slit from ear to ear.

210
00:13:12,250 --> 00:13:14,127
[GASPS] Amen.

211
00:13:15,795 --> 00:13:17,880
[TENCH]<i> Not only is this
exactly what we predicted,</i>

212
00:13:17,964 --> 00:13:20,049
but he's getting a taste
for it, there will be more.

213
00:13:20,133 --> 00:13:21,467
A sequence killer.

214
00:13:21,551 --> 00:13:22,802
A sequence killer?

215
00:13:22,885 --> 00:13:24,887
What we're calling it when
they kill three or more.

216
00:13:24,971 --> 00:13:28,391
Is this a new classification? Need
to get a steno to put it in writing.

217
00:13:28,474 --> 00:13:29,892
You bet. I'll talk to Marge.

218
00:13:30,435 --> 00:13:32,395
This is what you were talking
about with the Kemper thing?

219
00:13:32,478 --> 00:13:33,851
We briefed them with a description.

220
00:13:33,852 --> 00:13:35,481
We need to make sure they bring him in.

221
00:13:35,565 --> 00:13:38,359
- It's what we predicted.
- Thank you, Holden. I've been listening.

222
00:13:38,443 --> 00:13:41,779
- [TENCH] We have to make this right.
- I agree. You do now.

223
00:13:43,156 --> 00:13:45,825
What are you waiting for?
You got a plane to catch.

